Package mobilepad.io.message.control

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandEvent
    A type of control event containing a command to be executed in OS terminal
    ControlEvent
    A type of message containing data to control the system.
    CustomEvent
    An event to be paired with an input event in program GUI
    DisconnectEvent
    An event disconnecting currently paired device
    KeyCombinationEvent
    An event executing a combination of key presses
    KeyEvent
    An event executing single key press
    KeyEvent.Key
    Class containing static literals defining key codes for usage in the mobile application
    MouseButtonEvent
    An event executing mouse button press
    MouseButtonEvent.Button
    Class containing static literals for usage in mobile application
    MouseDoubleClickEvent
    An event executing double click of a specified mouse button
    MouseMoveEvent
    An event executing moving mouse to a specified location
    SwipeEvent
    Event sent when a swipe on screen was made in mobile application.
